    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "你有没有偷过酒？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我什么都没有偷过。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "我偷过。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "偷谁的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "偷我老子的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "我们家那位老爷子虽然不常喝酒，藏的却都是好酒，很可能比我们家藏的剑还好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你们家为什么不叫神酒山庄？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "因为我们家除了我之外都是君子，不是酒鬼。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "幸好你不是。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "幸好你也不是。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "我们家的藏酒虽好，只可惜我只偷了两次就被捉住了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "所以后来我只好去偷别人的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "偷谁的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "绿水湖对岸有家酒铺，掌柜的也姓谢，我早就知道他是个好人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以你就去偷他的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "偷风不偷月，偷雨不偷雪，偷好人不偷坏人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "这是偷王和偷祖宗传留下来的教训，要做小偷的人，就千万不可不记在心里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为就算被好人抓住了也没什么了不得，被坏人抓住可就有点不得了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "不是有点不得了，是大大的不得了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是好人也会抓小偷的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "所以我又被抓住了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "虽然没什么了不起，却也让我得到个教训。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "什么教训？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "要偷酒喝，最好让别人去偷，自己最多只能在外面望风！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好，这次我去偷，你望风！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    }
